<hr local-id=3D"51b0132a-d873-4285-bba4-7a3e5f2f85fa">
<h2 local-id=3D"a07ee06e5bfb" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-ExampleMinimal=
Request">Example Minimal Request</h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "query": "query { repo(name: \"repo1\") { ref(name: \"main\") { files { p=
ath } } } }"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"8a4c1707-bd9f-432e-acf3-fa87dce71543">
<h1 local-id=3D"40b5982eb394" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-ResponseFormat=
">Response Format</h1>
<p local-id=3D"97abca1f0e3d">The API returns a <strong>GraphQL-style respon=
se envelope</strong>.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "data": {},
  "errors": []
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"97258b36-e5d3-498f-bfed-8293f198e98a">
<h2 local-id=3D"39b78cc857cd" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-ResponseFields=
">Response Fields</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"center" data-local-id=3D"4f4=
63d37-a1c5-4f6c-ae52-d83186cda631" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6fa2ff64-4561-48c3-ac76-1cc90d158329">
<th data-local-id=3D"efff57a1-f1ec-442b-82e8-a20006eea093" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"7438dea0e665">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"a98d8266-bc35-4202-a9a8-5aa1b305640a" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3ef9199bad8f">Type</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"23e8a16b-05e5-4378-88fa-bf05401b874b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"6bb50e354ddd">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"32238548-06eb-46ef-9c11-8042a2ebf4e3">
<td data-local-id=3D"b5b052e9-107f-4353-bea2-d3e9e6dba17f" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"43e8fcb54a04">data</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dd76c5f6-8112-4eb9-a3c4-fc8b28aba2db" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"99774dc29f75">object</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3633752d-4379-4f75-9fe6-167889c02478" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f52e33d2824e">Query result structured according to the query=
 selection set</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"cbb8f379-730c-41b9-bb87-d2f16082c460">
<td data-local-id=3D"f541d9af-f799-4910-8f4d-06bbf767c0df" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e42c2d635aad">errors</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b5837f60-62ac-4d53-8383-c1b0a4601949" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b92c441f4741">array</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bcd1500d-8c8c-4b97-9a9b-931dde955d7d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"151ff3e8d255">List of errors that occurred during validation=
 or execution</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"eec1c0dd5978" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-SuccessfulQuer=
yExample">Successful Query Example</h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "data": {
    "repo": {
      "ref": {
        "file": {
          "artefacts": [
            {
              "symbolFqn": "AuthService.login",
              "canonicalKind": "METHOD"
            },
            {
              "symbolFqn": "AuthService.logout",
              "canonicalKind": "METHOD"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"155829e59f7d" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-ValidationErro=
rExample">Validation Error Example</h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "data": null,
  "errors": [
    {
      "message": "Cannot query field 'banana' on type 'Repo'.",
      "locations": [
        { "line": 3, "column": 5 }
      ],
      "extensions": {
        "code": "INVALID_FIELD"
      }
    }
  ]
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"7dcb2ca83c7e" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-PartialSuccess=
Example">Partial Success Example</h2>
<p local-id=3D"82a3a8b9d5f0">GraphQL-style responses may return <strong>par=
tial data when some fields fail</strong>.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "data": {
    "repo": {
      "ref": null
    }
  },
  "errors": [
    {
      "message": "Ref 'main' not found.",
      "path": ["repo", "ref"]
    }
  ]
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h1 local-id=3D"512d2d57d72c" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-AutocompleteMe=
tadataAPI">Autocomplete Metadata API</h1>
<p local-id=3D"5b0e6c739cd7">This section describes the request and respons=
e format used by the <strong>Query Explorer </strong> to retrieve <strong>s=
chema metadata</strong> for powering <strong>autocomplete assistance</stron=
g>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"25921344add7">The autocomplete system is <strong>schema-driv=
en</strong>, meaning the frontend retrieves queryable <strong>types, fields=
, and arguments</strong> from the backend and uses them to generate suggest=
ions based on the <strong>editor cursor position</strong>.</p>
<h1 local-id=3D"8e5e81f064f2" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-SchemaEndpoint=
">Schema Endpoint</h1>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"af=
49f912-8006-4b6d-88fc-b023202d718f" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ee079421-3be4-4a9a-b1a1-8b74782159df">
<th data-local-id=3D"1dfc3932-ecdd-4fb2-9ee6-9f728ea746e0" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"1c6343adaee1">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"ce1c9d92-03a0-45a6-bd52-ed7b3d85c7f7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3c9fc973e692">Value</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"17561d8a-beed-4ae0-abb6-be5691358c33">
<td data-local-id=3D"19f8ead6-b74d-4db4-ab4b-15ffa8f2c683" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d327569ebbe1">Method</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"c2b41c76-7783-4b8d-ace5-875142ea9906" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"d61dbeea85be"><code>GET</code></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"aaa22e6e-b141-46fb-a196-eb28c235fbec">
<td data-local-id=3D"c68f88fd-9c72-40e2-9f98-e43aaf18d9f6" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"08a6f2648c04">Path</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"58a6b35c-f855-46c7-b23b-3390da3e4798" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"1047992f6420"><code>/query-schema</code></p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"6793054e-69a2-4f9a-bc0e-20dc67a0a0f4">
<td data-local-id=3D"098d34d3-46b4-4e2a-9e43-29eac2d0ace3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"96d8e3c7f242">Content-Type</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"204d82a9-fcd3-409d-b219-763fb4d80868" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"07165679ab4a"><code>application/json</code></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"d4cce623ec7b">This endpoint returns metadata describing the =
<strong>query schema</strong>.<br>
 The frontend loads this schema when the <strong>Query Explorer initializes=
</strong> and caches it for the <strong>duration of the session</strong>.</=
p>
<h1 local-id=3D"a50b7e9ab857" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-Request">Reque=
st</h1>
<p local-id=3D"7dbdd4c780d9">The request is a simple <strong>GET call</stro=
ng>. No request body is required.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">GET /qu=
ery-schema</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h1 local-id=3D"4200c9cf4f60" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-ResponseFormat=
.1">Response Format</h1>
<p local-id=3D"317fb805984c">The response returns a <strong>schema metadata=
 object</strong> describing all <strong>queryable types and fields</strong>=
.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "Query": {
    "fields": {
      "repo": {
        "type": "Repo",
        "args": {
          "name": "String!"
        },
        "description": "Select a repository"
      },
      "search": {
        "type": "SearchResult",
        "args": {
          "query": "String!"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "Repo": {
    "fields": {
      "ref": {
        "type": "Ref",
        "args": {
          "name": "String!"
        }
      },
      "commit": {
        "type": "Commit",
        "args": {
          "sha": "String!"
        }
      },
      "files": {
        "type": "[File]",
        "args": {
          "path": "String"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "Ref": {
    "fields": {
      "file": {
        "type": "File",
        "args": {
          "path": "String!"
        }
      },
      "files": {
        "type": "[File]",
        "args": {
          "path": "String"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h1 local-id=3D"b91a1d09dadb" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-SchemaStructur=
e">Schema Structure</h1>
<p local-id=3D"0e55e0ba9d3c">Each <strong>schema type</strong> contains a l=
ist of fields.</p>
<p local-id=3D"df191e2590be">Field metadata includes:</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"1d=
e89042-f1bf-4a07-bbd7-45cabc0b8fa7" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"3bb4b88b-9136-4651-9da4-6c4b4f40ff72">
<th data-local-id=3D"302d935b-d171-408f-bccb-b278b91d0152" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"f9ad616aa117">Field</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f5ed0c77-e40e-4275-a3d6-709d126f65cd" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"4ce6a705b18c">Description</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"db9ec106-80d5-4a76-b15d-79505d7a18fa">
<td data-local-id=3D"639b8e76-99ef-4836-b12e-0c2b9ef4d9a5" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"393cafb621c3">type</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"086bbc1c-ac85-4a87-bc03-933fe1d11b38" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2dff1fdc4216">Return type of the field</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c39d0de0-873d-4359-b29c-1459edc11299">
<td data-local-id=3D"86ded88a-139f-43a3-9f39-889cf8055def" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"114b379665bb">args</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"f907cbf3-51b9-4b2f-a258-ec7e01269154" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c8b8831d5014">Arguments accepted by the field</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"385d04cc-eddc-4570-8783-28ccb3d6ea71">
<td data-local-id=3D"99ceb517-75c2-4241-9149-1e701d706b03" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c1a66b11b015">description</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d99342f1-0fdd-43bc-a070-516b5475daa7" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e5a77f016fa3">Optional documentation text</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 local-id=3D"2c231e0ba666" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-ExampleFieldDe=
finition">Example Field Definition</h2>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">{
  "type": "Repo",
  "args": {
    "name": "String!"
  },
  "description": "Select a repository"
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h1 local-id=3D"e7d32e4b077d" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-AutocompleteFl=
ow">Autocomplete Flow</h1>
<p local-id=3D"68d03682d6d1">The <strong>Query Explorer autocomplete system=
</strong> operates as follows:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">Query E=
xplorer loads
      =E2=86=93
GET /query-schema
      =E2=86=93
Schema cached in frontend state
      =E2=86=93
User types query
      =E2=86=93
Editor detects cursor position
      =E2=86=93
Frontend determines current query type
      =E2=86=93
Autocomplete suggestions generated</pre>
</div>
</div>
<h1 local-id=3D"491bb547aced" id=3D"QueryExplorerAPIContract-ExampleAutocom=
pleteScenario">Example Autocomplete Scenario</h1>
<p local-id=3D"96c7051a355c">User types:</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">query {
  repo(name: "repo1") {
    |
  }
}</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"94aaba06d0b2">The editor determines the <strong>current type=
 is </strong><code>Repo</code> and suggests fields from the <strong>Repo sc=
hema</strong>:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"19d17607-65ed-443c-8446-db5c54938ec8">
<li local-id=3D"c549a9de-8d32-486b-a714-27283ebb5593">
<p local-id=3D"d1a575e41f8e"><code>ref</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2e9ac468-0534-428e-995a-0a879204c0f5">
<p local-id=3D"846bf1504f04"><code>commit</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"581f8ab8-69c9-4497-9899-49f0f11e8dfa">
<p local-id=3D"ecc1ec43fe24"><code>files</code></p></li>
</ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
